imdb.plot outline: "The condemned world champion" is a personal documentary about a former elite swimmer and pro boxer Mikaela Lauren. The story unfolds her journey from an convicted criminal to an world champion in boxing. A close depiction of someone who got a second chance in life, done with its past, got revenge and live today as a strong role model for many, especially for young girls.
